lead_paragraph: The Romanian Football Federation (FRF) has decided to appoint a foreigner to replace Anghel Iordanescu as the national team’s coach, the ruling body's president said on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Romania to Appoint First Foreign Coach Since 1934
headline.main: Romania to Appoint First Foreign Coach Since 1934
